__SqlaTable__.sql:
with 
defilter as (
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_topproducts
union
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_locwisesku_seg_cate_brand
),
aa as (
select 
sd.skuid,sd.locationid,sd.demanddate,sd.staticweekno,coalesce(sd.demand,0) totalsalesunit, coalesce(sd.demand * sd.lastknownrrp,0) totalsalesamt,null as dailylowerci,null as dailyupperci,
df.SelectGroup,df.categories,df.store
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek sd
join defilter df on  df.skuid=sd.skuid and df.locationid = sd.locationid
where 
sd.staticweekno between 0 and 5
and sd.demanddate::date < now()::date 
union all
select 
sd.skuid,sd.locationid,sd.forecastdate,sd.staticweekno,coalesce(sd.peakforecast,0) totalforecastunit,coalesce(sd.peakforecast*sd.lastknownrrp,0) totalforecastamt , sd.dailylowerci,sd.dailyupperci,
df.SelectGroup,df.categories,df.store
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek sd 
join defilter df on  df.skuid=sd.skuid and df.locationid = sd.locationid
where 
sd.staticweekno between 0 and 3
and sd.forecastdate::date >= now()::date 
)
select * from 
aa 
where 
 skuid = {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('skuid')) + "'" }}
and selectgroup={{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('selectgroup')) + "'" }}
and categories ={{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('categories')) + "'" }} 
and store = {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('store')) + "'" }}

select locationid,locationvariant1,locationvariant1||'-'||locationid as store from 
demandai.location_metadata lm
where
lm.locationstatus=true and 
lm.ispeakrowdelete is null

with 
supplydt as 
(
select sd.skuid,sd.locationid,min(sd.resupplydate) latestsupplydat from demandai.sku_loc_resupply sd
where
sd.resupplydate >= now()::date
and sd.ispeakrowdelete is null
group by sd.skuid,sd.locationid 
)
,
lwsales as (
select 
skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend,coalesce(sum(wg1.demand),0) totalsalesunit
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek wg1
where 
staticweekno =1
group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend
),
currweksales as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend,coalesce(sum(wg1.demand),0) totalsalesunit
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek wg1
where 
staticweekno = 0
group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend
)
,
currforecastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) totalforecastunit
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno =0
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
),
nextforecastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) as forecastsaleunitnextweek
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno =1
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
)
,
next2forecastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) as forecastsaleunit2nextweek
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno =2
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
)
,
next3forecastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) as forecastsaleunit3nextweek
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno =3
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
)
,
defilter as (
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_topproducts
union
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_locwisesku_seg_cate_brand
)
select
sd.postcode,sd.currentstock as "CurrentStock",
lw.totalsalesunit "Lastweeksales" ,fcw.totalforecastunit "Currentweekforecastsales",
cw.totalsalesunit "Currentweeksalesachieved",
fnw.forecastsaleunitnextweek as "Forecasednextweek1",
fnw2.forecastsaleunit2nextweek as "Forecasednextweek2",
fnw3.forecastsaleunit3nextweek as "Forecasednextweek3",
slr.resupplyunit as "ResupplyUnit",
slr.latestsupplydat  as "Resupplydate",
case when 
coalesce(fnw.forecastsaleunitnextweek-(coalesce(sd.currentstock,0) + coalesce(slr.resupplyunit,0)),0) > 0 then 
coalesce(fnw.forecastsaleunitnextweek-(coalesce(sd.currentstock,0) + coalesce(slr.resupplyunit,0)),0) else null end 
as "AIRecommendationNextorder",
sd.name as "ProductName",sd.skuid as "SKUID",sd.locationid,
sd.demanddate,
df.SelectGroup,df.categories,df.store
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek sd
join defilter df on  df.skuid=sd.skuid and df.locationid = sd.locationid
left join lwsales lw on lw.skuid=sd.skuid and lw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join currweksales cw on cw.skuid=sd.skuid and cw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join currforecastweksale fcw on fcw.skuid=sd.skuid and fcw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join nextforecastweksale fnw on fnw.skuid=sd.skuid and fnw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join next2forecastweksale fnw2 on fnw2.skuid=sd.skuid and fnw2.locationid = sd.locationid
left join next3forecastweksale fnw3 on fnw3.skuid=sd.skuid and fnw3.locationid = sd.locationid
left join (
	select supplydt.skuid,supplydt.locationid,sr.resupplyamount as resupplyunit , supplydt.latestsupplydat 
    from supplydt 
    inner join demandai.sku_loc_resupply sr on sr.skuid = supplydt.skuid   and sr.locationid = supplydt.locationid and sr.resupplydate = supplydt.latestsupplydat
    where sr.ispeakrowdelete is null
		  ) slr on slr.skuid=sd.skuid and slr.locationid = sd.locationid 
where 
sd.demanddate = now()::date -3
and df.SelectGroup = {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('selectgroup')) + "'" }}
  and df.categories= {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('categories')) + "'" }}
  and df.store= {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('store')) + "'" }}
 and sd.skuid = {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('skuid')) + "'" }}
order by name

with 
supplydt as 
(
select sd.skuid,sd.locationid,min(sd.resupplydate) latestsupplydat from demandai.sku_loc_resupply sd
where
sd.resupplydate >= now()::date
and sd.ispeakrowdelete is null
group by sd.skuid,sd.locationid 
),
lwsales as 
(
select 
skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend,coalesce(sum(wg1.demand),0) totalsales, coalesce(sum(wg1.demand * wg1.lastknownrrp),0) totalsalesamt
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek wg1
where 
staticweekno =1
group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend
),
currweksales as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend,coalesce(sum(wg1.demand * wg1.lastknownrrp),0) totalsalesamt
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek wg1
where 
staticweekno = 0
group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,weekend
)
, 
forecastlastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) totalforecast,coalesce(sum(peakforecast*lastknownrrp),0) totalforecastamount
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno = -1
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
),
nextforecastweksale as (
select skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart,coalesce(sum(peakforecast),0) as forecastsaleunitnextweek,
coalesce(sum(peakforecast*lastknownrrp),0) totalforecastamount
from  demandai.mvw_sku_forecast_with_lastrrp_staticweek
 where 
 staticweekno =1
 group by skuid,locationid,staticweekno,weekstart
),
defilter as (
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_topproducts
union
select locationid,skuid,SelectGroup,categories,store from demandai.vw_de_locwisesku_seg_cate_brand
)
select 
sd.name as "ProductName",sd.skuid as "SKUID",sd.category as "Category",
sd.peakcategory1 as "AISegmentRevenue",sd.peakcategory2 as "AISegmentForecast",
lw.totalsales "SalesUnitLastWeek" ,lw.totalsalesamt "SalesAmountLastWeek" ,
-- round(((fcw.totalforecast*100)/lw.totalsales),2) "%age of Forecasted unit sold",
sd.currentstock as "CurrentStock",slr.resupplyunit as "SupplyUnit",
sd.storedesiredstockduration as "AIweekofSuppy",
fnw.forecastsaleunitnextweek as "AIpredicteddemand",
ci.dailylowerci as "LowerCI",
ci.dailyupperci as "UpperCI",
case when sd.demandgrowth is not null then round((sd.demandgrowth*100),2)|| '%' else null end as "DemandVariation",
case 
when sd.currentstock < sd.minstocklevel then 'understock'
when sd.currentstock > sd.maxstocklevel then 'overstock'
else null end as "StockStatus",
sd.demanddate,sd.locationid,
df.SelectGroup,df.categories,df.store
from 
demandai.mvw_weekly_demand_staticweek sd
join defilter df on  df.skuid=sd.skuid and df.locationid = sd.locationid
left join lwsales lw on lw.skuid=sd.skuid and lw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join currweksales cw on cw.skuid=sd.skuid and cw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join forecastlastweksale fcw on fcw.skuid=sd.skuid and fcw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join nextforecastweksale fnw on fnw.skuid=sd.skuid and fnw.locationid = sd.locationid
left join (
	select supplydt.skuid,supplydt.locationid,sr.resupplyamount as resupplyunit , supplydt.latestsupplydat 
    from supplydt 
    inner join demandai.sku_loc_resupply sr on sr.skuid = supplydt.skuid   and sr.locationid = supplydt.locationid and sr.resupplydate = supplydt.latestsupplydat
    where sr.ispeakrowdelete is null
		  ) slr on slr.skuid=sd.skuid and slr.locationid = sd.locationid 
left join (
	select sf.skuid,sf.locationid,sf.peakforecastmeta1 as dailylowerci , sf.peakforecastmeta2 as dailyupperci
	from demandai.sku_loc_forecasts sf 
	where sf.forecastdate =now()::date
	and sf.ispeakrowdelete is null
			) ci on ci.skuid=sd.skuid and ci.locationid = sd.locationid 
where 
sd.demanddate = now()::date -1
  and df.SelectGroup = {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('selectgroup')) + "'" }}
  and df.categories= {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('categories')) + "'" }}
  and df.store= {{ "'" + "','".join(filter_values('store')) + "'" }}
order by name
